has won 19 PGA events and offers years of experience in coaching and developing players. Matt Carter a young dynamic Professional, Matt is still concentrating on his golf career and is participating in the NSW Pro AM circuit.\r\n\r\nBook online or give us a call on 4261 1647'),(85,10,'_callout_three','field_57de35d9a2ff0'),(86,33,'hero_slider','a:1:{i:0;s:2:\"16\";}'),(87,33,'_hero_slider','field_57de2c69c6d57'),(88,33,'gallery_items','a:1:{i:0;s:2:\"16\";}'),(89,33,'_gallery_items','field_57de310827b2d'),(90,33,'images','1'),(91,33,'_images','field_57de32ce051dc'),(92,33,'callout_one','<h1>The Grange Golf Club tees up Troon with $7m make-over</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nThe world’s largest golf management company set to deliver a new golfing and events experience to the Illawarra\r\n\r\nIllawarra, NSW, 1st June, 2016 – The NSW South Coast’s leading golf club, The Grange, and amalgamated events partner, Dapto Leagues, has today signed an exclusive deal with Troon®, the leader in upscale golf facility management, development and marketing, as part of a strategic $7m refurbishment of the Grange clubhouse, function facilities and golf course.'),(93,33,'_callout_one','field_57de3588a2fee'),(94,33,'callout_two','<h1>Membership</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nAs a Dapto Leagues Club &amp; Grange Golf Club Member, you will gain access to our extensive Club Facilities including cafe’s, restaurants, bars, entertainment and promotions.\r\n\r\nWith your Dapto Leagues Rewards club card you will also have access to VIP benefits at hundreds of local retails, when you look at the value, there’s never been a better time to join the club.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.google.com.au\">sign up</a>'),(95,33,'_callout_two','field_57de35d2a2fef'),(96,33,'callout_three','<h1>Book a lesson</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nIf you’re looking for a little golfing help then our Golf Club Professionals Rob McKay and Matt Carter are happy to help with a lesson or two.\r\n\r\nRob became a professional in 1966 and at the time was the youngest qualified professional in Australia; Rob has won 19 PGA events and offers years of experience in coaching and developing players. Matt Carter a young dynamic Professional, Matt is still concentrating on his golf career and is participating in the NSW Pro AM circuit.\r\n\r\nBook online or give us a call on 4261 1647\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.google.com.au\">booking form</a>'),(97,33,'_callout_three','field_57de35d9a2ff0'),(98,34,'_edit_last','1'),(99,34,'slide_template','default'),(100,34,'_edit_lock','1476140934:1'),(107,12,'callout_one','<h1>Ceremonies</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nExperience the magic of the Grange, a perfect country setting with a choice of elegant outdoor rooms perfect to say “I do”.'),(108,12,'_callout_one','field_57de3588a2fee'),(109,12,'callout_two','<h1>Inspiring New Ways</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nDesigned with grace and understated elegance in mind. The Grange a picturesque Hamptons Style venue.\r\n\r\nYour guests will be impressed by Our Marble Bar framed with custom designed shutters, furnished with Australian and Italian furniture, Replica Tom Dixon Etch Web Gold Pendants, and featuring a 1908 Mahogany wood Baby Grand Piano.\r\n\r\nThe Grange is lined with white French doors and windows, deep veranda\'s and manicured gardens.\r\n\r\nElegant white Cathedral chairs, fine glassware, exquisitely designed menu by Executive Chef, Donald Flanagan, accompanied by prestigious local and imported wines, delivered by handpicked warm, friendly, efficient \'service with a smile\'.\r\n\r\nThe Grange is complete with your personal, private bridal suite. Diamond print Dove velvet chaise and ottoman, romantic bureau French Style white dressing table, mirrored buffet and Verre glass ring feature pendant.\r\n\r\nThe Grange truly is, <em>inspiring new ways</em>'),(110,12,'_callout_two','field_57de35d2a2fef'),(111,12,'callout_three','<h1>Tour &amp; Taste</h1>\r\n<form action=\"https://www.salesforce.com/servlet/servlet.WebToLead?encoding=UTF-8\" method=\"POST\">Join us for one of our wedding open days\r\n<h3><strong>OPEN DAY</strong><strong>\r\n<span style=\"color: #808080;\">Friday 6 April &amp; Friday 4 May 2018</span></strong>\r\nBY REGISTRATION ONLY</h3>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><em>To Register we need:</em></strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #339966;\"><strong>Your Full Name, Mobile, Email and How Many Guests will be attending</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"mailto:info@thegrangegolfclub.com.au\" target=\"_blank\">info@thegrangegolfclub.com.au</a>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</form><!--more-->'),(112,12,'_callout_three','field_57de35d9a2ff0'),(113,40,'callout_one','<h1>Ceremonies</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nThe Grange Golf Club offers the perfect lush green outdoor setting to say “I do” and celebrate your nuptials with family and friends. Maybe the 10th tee, the terrace or the manicured lawn of the 18th tee.\r\n\r\nPlease contact our Event Team who will be more than happy to take you on a walk around our beautiful grounds to assist in choosing your perfect location.'),(114,40,'_callout_one','field_57de3588a2fee'),(115,40,'callout_two','<h1>Reception</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nYour Award Winning Event Team would be delighted to help you achieve a truly memorable day whichever venue you choose The Grange or The Sinclair. We will explore all avenues to ensure that what you imagine is delivered to perfection from room and ceremony decorations, menu and beverage selections to entertainment.\r\n\r\nThe Grange provides an ideal location to host both your Ceremony and Reception, tucked in amongst the beautiful sprawling greens and only minutes from Wollongong.\r\n\r\nA long held reputation for personalised and friendly service makes The Grange a perfect venue for your wedding. To discuss your Special Day at the Grange please contact our Event Coordinator on 4261 1333 to arrange a suitable time.'),(116,40,'_callout_two','field_