ing locations for you to say your I DO’s. After your ceremony the photo opportunities on the golf course will have your photographer very excited. To discuss your special day simply book an appointment through our website or call our Functions Manager on 02 4261 1647. '),(1708,358,'_callout_two','field_57de35d2a2fef'),(1709,358,'callout_three','<h1>Tour &amp; Taste</h1>\r\n<form action=\"https://www.salesforce.com/servlet/servlet.WebToLead?encoding=UTF-8\" method=\"POST\"><input name=\"oid\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"00D28000001PgQh\" />\r\n<input name=\"retURL\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"http://http://www.thegrangegolfclub.com.au/golf/thank-you/\" />\r\n<input id=\"first_name\" maxlength=\"40\" name=\"first_name\" size=\"20\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"First Name\" />\r\n<input id=\"last_name\" maxlength=\"80\" name=\"last_name\" size=\"20\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Last Name\" />\r\n<input id=\"00N2800000EJqax\" maxlength=\"255\" name=\"00N2800000EJqax\" required=\"true\" size=\"20\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Mobile\" />\r\n<input id=\"00N2800000EJqjB\" maxlength=\"255\" name=\"00N2800000EJqjB\" required=\"true\" size=\"20\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Email\" />\r\n<input id=\"zip\" maxlength=\"20\" name=\"zip\" size=\"20\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Postcode\" /><label></label>\r\n\r\n<input name=\"submit\" type=\"submit\" />\r\n\r\n</form>'),(1710,358,'_callout_three','field_57de35d9a2ff0'),(1711,358,'content','<h1>MEET YOUR WEDDING SPECIALIST</h1>\r\n&nbsp;'),(1712,358,'_content','field_57de46825b148'),(1713,358,'image',''),(1714,358,'_image','field_57de50b27e77f'),(1715,359,'evcal_event_color_n','1'),(1717,359,'_edit_last','1'),(1718,359,'_edit_lock','1478148173:2'),(1723,359,'evcal_event_color','206177'),(1724,359,'evo_location_tax_id','5'),(1725,359,'evcal_subtitle','We\'re having a Wedding Tour & Taste'),(1726,359,'evcal_hide_locname','no'),(1727,359,'evcal_gmap_gen','yes'),(1728,359,'evcal_repeat','no'),(1729,359,'_evcal_rep_series','no'),(1730,359,'ev