<h1>Reception</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nDesigned with grace and understated elegance in mind. The Grange set upon extensive renovations during 2016 and now resembles a picturesque modern Country Club House. Our wedding space has a warm and welcoming feeling with an abundance of natural lighting, surrounded by a beautiful paved under covered terrace area where wedding guests can enjoy views over the sprawling greens. Our Internationally acclaimed Executive Chef Donald Flanagan has designed a menu of exceptional quality that is sure to please your wedding guests. Our Functions Manager will arrange a private menu tasting for you, to tailor your wedding menu to your preferences. If you are hosting your ceremony at The Grange than we have breathtaking locations for you to say your I DO’s. After your ceremony the photo opportunities on the golf course will have your photographer very excited. To discuss your special day simply book an appointment through our website or call our Functions Manager on 02 4261 1647. '),(1809,378,'_callout_two','field_57de35d2a2fef'),(1810,378,'callout_three','<h1 style=\"font-family:\'centrale sans\';\">Tour &amp; Taste</h1>\r\n<form action=\"https://www.salesforce.com/servlet/servlet.WebToLead?encoding=UTF-8\" method=\"POST\"><input name=\"oid\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"00D28000001PgQh\" />\r\n<input name=\"retURL\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"http://http://www.thegrangegolfclub.com.au/golf/thank-you/\" />\r\n<input id=\"first_name\" maxlength=\"40\" name=\"first_name\" size=\"20\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"First Name\" />\r\n<input id=\"last_name\" maxlength=\"80\" name=\"last_name\" size=\"20\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Last Name\" />\r\n<input id=\"00N2800000EJqax\" maxlength=\"255\" name=\"00N2800000EJqax\" required=\"true\" size=\"20\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Mobile\" />\r\n<input id=\"00N2800000EJqjB\" maxlength=\"255\" name=\"00N2800000EJqjB\" required=\"true\" size=\"20\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Email\" />\r\n<input id=\"zip\"