7,'hero_slider','a:1:{i:0;s:2:\"16\";}'),(4188,627,'_hero_slider','field_57de2c69c6d57'),(4189,627,'gallery_items','a:1:{i:0;s:2:\"16\";}'),(4190,627,'_gallery_items','field_57de310827b2d'),(4191,627,'images','1'),(4192,627,'_images','field_57de32ce051dc'),(4193,627,'callout_one','<h1>The Grange Golf Club tees up Troon with $7m make-over</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nThe world’s largest golf management company set to deliver a new golfing and events experience to the Illawarra\r\n\r\nIllawarra, NSW, 1st June, 2016 – The NSW South Coast’s leading golf club, The Grange, and amalgamated events partner, Dapto Leagues, has today signed an exclusive deal with Troon®, the leader in upscale golf facility management, development and marketing, as part of a strategic $7m refurbishment of the Grange clubhouse, function facilities and golf course.'),(4194,627,'_callout_one','field_57de3588a2fee'),(4195,627,'callout_two','<h1>Membership</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nAs a Dapto Leagues Club &amp; Grange Golf Club Member, you will gain access to our extensive Club Facilities including cafe’s, restaurants, bars, entertainment and promotions.\r\n\r\nWith your Dapto Leagues Rewards club card you will also have access to VIP benefits at hundreds of local retails, when you look at the value, there’s never been a better time to join the club.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/the-grange-golf-club/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/25210748/Illawarra_DLC_Directory_June_2016_Draft.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">sign up</a>'),(4196,627,'_callout_two','field_57de35d2a2fef'),(4197,627,'callout_three','<h1>Book a lesson</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nIf you’re looking for a little golfing help then our Golf Club Professionals Rob McKay and Matt Carter are happy to help with a lesson or two.\r\n\r\nRob became a professional in 1966 and at the time was the youngest qualified professional in Australia; Rob has won 19 PGA events and offers years of experience in coaching and developing players. Matt Carter a young dynamic Professional, Matt is still concentrating on his golf career and is participating in the NSW Pro AM circuit.\r\n\r\nBook online or give us a call on 4261 1647'),(4198,627,'_callout_three','field_57de35d9a2ff0'),(4199,627,'content','<h1>Golf Course</h1>\r\n<strong>**Please note that due to the recent weather, the Golf Course is closed until further inspection on Monday 10 April**</strong>\r\nThe picturesque Mullet Creek winds its way through the course. The gently undulating and more heavily tree-lined back nine presents The Grange’s most memorable holes. The land rolls and dips and the 532 metre par-5 13th is a brute – not just for its length but also its demand for accuracy to avoid the rows of tall trees lining the fairway.\r\n\r\nWhile The Grange’s longest hole requires straight hitting, so does its shortest. The 146 metre par 3 18th is the club’s signature hole – and for good reason. Standing on the tee there is only one thing between you the front edge the green – the cool, flowing waters of Mullet Creek. There is a short fairway to the left of the water and in front of putting surface, which is heavily bunkered. This hole is easily affected by wind and anything from a 3-iron to a wedge could be used to find the small undulating green.'),(4200,627,'_content','field_57de46825b148'),(4201,627,'image',''),(4202,627,'_image','field_57de50b27e77f'),(4203,627,'callout_two_background',''),(4204,627,'_callout_two_background','field_58378ff6e5817'),(4205,628,'hero_slider','a:1:{i:0;s:2:\"16\";}'),(4206,628,'_hero_slider','field_57de2c69c6d57'),(4207,628,'gallery_items','a:1:{i:0;s:2:\"16\";}'),(4208,628,'_gallery_items','field_57de310827b2d'),(4209,628,'images','1'),(4210,628,'_images','field_57de32ce051dc'),(4211,628,'callout_one','<h1>The Grange Golf Club tees up Troon with $7m make-over</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nThe world’s largest golf management company set to deliver a new golfing and events experience to the Illawarra\r\n\r\nIllawarra, NSW, 1