ng yet accessible course, stunning natural surrounds and world-class events and hospitality.\r\n\r\nIn June, 2006, The Grange amalgamated with Dapto Leagues Club, sharing its vision to enhance both clubs for the benefits of locals and members and to become the leading venues in quality hospitality and customer service, whilst remaining financially secure and socially responsible.\r\n\r\nWith a major refurbishment taking place in 2016 in partnership with Troon Golf, The Grange is set to cement its position as one of NSW’s premier golf clubs, deliver more for locals and drive increased domestic and international tourism to the Illawarra region.\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Troon</h2>\r\nHeadquartered in Scottsdale, Ariz., Troon is the world’s largest golf management company, with more than 250 golf courses in its portfolio. Also specializing in homeowner association management, private residence clubs, estate management and associated hospitality venues, the company oversees operations at Troon Golf®, Honours Golf and Troon Privé properties located in 38 states and 31 countries.\r\n\r\nAdditionally, there are 56 Troon affiliated properties featuring 75 courses that have been recipients of a “Top 100” ranking by national and international publications.\r\n\r\nHeadquartered in Geneva, Switzerland and Dubai UAE, Troon’s International division is committed to developing Troon’s presence throughout the world. This rapidly expanding division now oversees operations at 44 courses in 16 countries including Australia, the United Arab Emirates, England, Russia and Spain with further expansion planned across all regions. www.Troon.com.\r\n\r\nTroon properties include Princeville Makai Golf Club, Kauai, Hawaii; Centurion Club, Hemel Hempstead, Hertfordshire, England; The Westin La Paloma Resort &amp; Spa, Tucson, Ariz.; The Bay Club, Berlin, Md.; Prince’s Golf Club, Sandwich, England; and Costa Baja Golf Club, in La Paz, Mexico.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Scott McCaw - Grange Golf Manager</h2>\r\nScott brings more than 16 years experience to The Grange in managing upscale golf operations internationally. Scott has worked in Abu Dhabi, Morocco and Azores managing internationally recognised golf courses including Saadiyat Beach Golf Club.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-481\" src=\"http://thegrangegolfclub.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/The-Grange-Food-8-16-1029-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"the-grange-food-8-16-1029\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />','About','','publish','closed','closed','','about','','','2017-04-27 16:53:42','2017-04-27 06:53:42','',10,'http://thegrangegolfclub.com.au/?page_id=162',0,'page','',0),(163,3,'2016-09-21 09:50:39','2016-09-20 23:50:39','','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','162-revision-v1','','','2016-09-21 09:50:39','2016-09-20 23:50:39','',162,'http://thegrangegolfclub.com.au/162-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(164,3,'2016-09-21 09:50:46','2016-09-20 23:50:46','About Page','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','162-revision-v1','','','2016-09-21 09:50:46','2016-09-20 23:50:46','',162,'http://thegrangegolfclub.com.au/162-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(167,3,'2016-09-21 09:53:08','2016-09-20 23:53:08','Bar and Café: 9am – 5pm\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thegrangegolfclub.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/All-Day-Menu.pdf\">all day menu</a>\r\nFriday Nights at The Grange\r\nEarly Dinner Seating from 5:30pm\r\nLate Dinner Seating from 7.00 pm\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-571\" src=\"http://thegrangegolfclub.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Friday-Nights-at-the-Grange-10Feb17-simple-correct-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"friday-nights-at-the-grange-10feb17-simple-correct\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://user-oeDdhLs.cld.bz/Friday-Night-Brasserie-Menu\">Friday Night Brasserie Menu</a>','Bar & Cafe','','publish','closed','closed','','bar-brasserie','','','2017-10-16 10:40:22','2017-10-15 23:40:22','',10,'http://thegrangegolfclub.com.au/?page_id=167',0,'page','',0),